# CODEOWNERS — review routing
#
# Every PR auto-requests review from the listed owner. For a solo repo
# this just makes the bookkeeping visible; when collaborators join, the
# entries scope to the area they're responsible for.
#
# Syntax: <pattern>  <@github-handles or emails>
# Later entries override earlier ones — most-specific wins.

